description: Italians weren't always lucky, but they did have occasional luck! Lucky Italian Numbers will help you pick those lucky numbers that might change your life! You can utter "Get a lucky number" or "Get X lucky numbers". Do what you will with the numbers, up to 10 lucky numbers! Forgettaboutit
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Lucky Italian Numbers to Give me my lucky number.
Alexa, ask Lucky Italian Numbers to Give me a lucky number.
Alexa, ask Lucky Italian Numbers to give me 6 lucky numbers.
name: Lucky Italian Numbers
shortDescription: Get a lucky number at random or get X amount of lucky numbers
